ave said some outlandish things on those boards but I never really mean them.  It is trash talk ask backalley or niivag I can trash talk with the best of them.<br>
<br>
What really blew me away guys is you were so quick to scold me but not the people who came here and quickly turned your website into a rant section.  Yes I was quick to defend backalley and would do so on any given day.  I value my friendships.  I apologized to talula.  It should be all over with.  Another thing that blew my mind is I defended your house.  This is IV's house and you do not disrespect it.  Same goes for my guild's website.  That nonsense should have been taken to the prexus boards, but fallen alliance chose here.  I freely admit I am no saint in this mess.  But I did not come to your site and start flaming left and right.  I added to something that backalley said, and I was wrong.  <br>
<br>
If you guys are gonna hold what I posted on a rant section over my head than I dont know what to do.  That is all water under the bridge to me.  Trash Talk happens in sports and in work and lord knows here.  For a group of people to do a 180 over such a silly matter that was not started by me is beyond me.  Then supporting FA in doing it.  Oh well whatever all I can say is I am sorry it ended up on your website.  I  respect you guys and what you do I have avidly preached that.  Then today got hung out like last years laundry.<br>
<br>
Anyways you guys have a great week, and I will see some of you in game.  Backalley sorry this got so blown out of proportion <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  Sometimes and you know me I try to do the right thing and it backfires.  I was defending you and your guild.  Nothing more nothing less.  In my opinion what they did was pretty scandalous.  I can take the flames Backalley you know that.  But what I cannot deal with is how only I am reprimanded when anyone could see they instigated this insanity here.  The prexus msg board had nothing to do with anyone but me.<br>
<br>
I apologize to you guys,  I am not perfect Backalley you know that, but I am very protective of my friends and I consider you and Niivag friends, as well as others in IV.<br>
<br>
Sincerely,<br>
<br>
Ianthia Foehammer <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/uanonagnome.showPublicProfile?language=EN>anonagnome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(11/13/01 11:46:38 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sorry to all in IV</span><hr size=1> Hello all,<br>
